{"title":"女瓦工","authors":["臧克家"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":4,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"女瓦工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"臧克家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶毒太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手脚上下忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸上蒸汗气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"薄雾透红光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淘米和面手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来搅灰泥浆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长锨像根针，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到手没分两。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转眼人不见，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚踏瓦片响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屋脊当马骑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑声响铃铛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久炼臂似铁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手巧胆子壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青天也能上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梯子不够长！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴雨别威风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和天争短长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“屋漏我来补！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似补衣裳。（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔徐启雄播图〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}